<text top="1872" left="1568" width="600" height="52" font="font19" id="p1_t99" reading_order_no="104" segment_no="6" tag_type="text">Kaowthumrong,  N.  Lee,  and  W. </text>
<text top="1920" left="1567" width="603" height="57" font="font11" id="p1_t100" reading_order_no="105" segment_no="6" tag_type="text">Lovett  [3].  Each  block  includes </text>
<text top="1972" left="1567" width="610" height="55" font="font3" id="p1_t101" reading_order_no="106" segment_no="6" tag_type="text">an  embedded  computer  (one  of </text>
